OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772107375
OL,3,CMan sent offensive posts to Reform
OL,4,Ccandidate standing in by-election in
OL,5,C2024
OL,7,FA man who sent offensive online
OL,8,Fmessages to a former MP during a by-
OL,9,Felection has been given a 12-month
OL,10,Fcommunity order.
OL,12,FZafar Hussain, 25, sent the posts to
OL,13,Fpolitician Simon Danczuk's Facebook
OL,14,Faccount ahead of the Rochdale by-
OL,15,Felection in February 2024.
OL,17,FThe former Labour MP was standing as a
OL,18,FReform party candidate.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
