FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772107375
OL,3,CMan sent offensive posts to Reform
OL,4,Ccandidate standing in by-election in
OL,5,C2024
OL,7,FHussain, of Kellett Street, Rochdale,
OL,8,Fsent a video of himself holding a
OL,9,FReform leaflet and stated "I'm gonna
OL,10,Fput one in his f****** head."
OL,12,FHe also called Mr Danczuk "a bald
OL,13,Fb******" and "an ugly, Zionist, church
OL,14,Fmember b******", as well as
OL,15,Fcommenting: "How dare you send such
OL,16,Fleaflets in our community? You will
OL,17,Fnever win. You will never get the
OL,18,FAsian vote you ugly, bald, f*******
OL,19,FPhil Mitchell-looking b******."
OL,26,@uD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
