FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772107375
OL,3,CMan sent offensive posts to Reform
OL,4,Ccandidate standing in by-election in
OL,5,C2024
OL,7,FManchester Magistrates Court heard a
OL,8,Freference to Reform as "white devils"
OL,9,Fwas also made.
OL,11,FMr Danczuk, reported the messages to
OL,12,Fthe police and Hussain was arrested.
OL,14,FWhen interviewed, he claimed the video
OL,15,Fhad been uploaded to a private
OL,16,FSnapchat group meant as "banter for
OL,17,Fhis boys".
OL,26,@pD@XOUpD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
