PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772107375
OL,3,CMan sent offensive posts to Reform
OL,4,Ccandidate standing in by-election in
OL,5,C2024
OL,7,FHussain denied being antisemetic and
OL,8,Fsaid he had been drinking alcohol, had
OL,9,Fnot taken his medication and had
OL,10,Fmental health issues after he
OL,11,Fsustained a bleed on the brain
OL,12,Ffollowing an attack in 2022.
OL,14,FHe later pleaded guilty to sending a
OL,15,Fgrossly offensive, menacing message
OL,16,Fcontrary to the Communications Act.
OL,18,FIn a victim statement read to the
OL,19,Fcourt, Mr Danczuk said he felt
OL,20,F"extremely concerned about the safety
OL,21,Fof myself and my family."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772107375
OL,3,CMan sent offensive posts to Reform
OL,4,Ccandidate standing in by-election in
OL,5,C2024
OL,7,FHe said security arrangements had to
OL,8,Fbe put in place but engagement with
OL,9,Fthe public during the election
OL,10,Fcampaign was "inevitably reduced"
OL,11,Fbecause he did not know what the
OL,12,Fperpetrator looked like.
OL,14,FHe added: "All this upheaval and
OL,15,Fintimidation had an adverse impact on
OL,16,Four campaign."
OL,18,FSentencing, District Judge James Hulse
OL,19,Ftold the defendant: "You received a
OL,20,Fleaflet that upset you and chose the
OL,21,Fmost abhorrent way to react to that.
OL,26,@{D@UOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
