FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772107375
OL,3,CMan sent offensive posts to Reform
OL,4,Ccandidate standing in by-election in
OL,5,C2024
OL,7,F"In terms of politicians being able to
OL,8,Fdo what is required, without that we
OL,9,Fhave a very different society where
OL,10,Fthey feel so threatened that they
OL,11,Fcannot go about their business."
OL,13,FHe said the offence was racially
OL,14,Faggravated because of the defendant's
OL,15,Freference to "white devils", and noted
OL,16,Fthat Hussein, who has no previous
OL,17,Fconvictions, was "contrite and honest"
OL,18,Fin his pre-sentence report interview.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
