PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772107375
OL,3,CMan sent offensive posts to Reform
OL,4,Ccandidate standing in by-election in
OL,5,C2024
OL,7,FHussain, was given a 12-month
OL,8,Fcommunity order, and is required to
OL,9,Fcomplete 120 hours of unpaid work and
OL,10,F15 days of rehabilitation activities.
OL,12,FHe was also given a 12 month
OL,13,Frestraining order to prevent contact
OL,14,Fwith Mr Danczuk.
OL,16,FBefore he left the dock, Hussain told
OL,17,Fthe judge: "I'm not racist. I've got
OL,18,Fwhite cousins."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
