PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772107375
OL,3,CMan sent offensive posts to Reform
OL,4,Ccandidate standing in by-election in
OL,5,C2024
OL,7,FFollowing the hearing Mr Danczuk
OL,8,Fslammed the sentence, saying he
OL,9,Fbelieved "weak sentencing...
OL,10,Fencourages this sort of extremist
OL,11,Fbehaviour".
OL,13,FMr Danczuk said: "This was
OL,14,Fsectarianism at its worst. I think he
OL,15,Fshould have got a custodial sentence,
OL,16,Fit was an opportunity for the
OL,17,Fjudiciary to send a clear message to
OL,18,Fextremists who disrupt Parliamentary
OL,19,Felections and they have missed this
OL,20,Fopportunity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
