PN,39209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772107375
OL,3,CMan sent offensive posts to Reform
OL,4,Ccandidate standing in by-election in
OL,5,C2024
OL,7,F"This had a major impact on our
OL,8,Fcampaign, it created real fear amongst
OL,9,Four activists and members of my
OL,10,Ffamily, and I don't think the sentence
OL,11,Fwas strong enough.
OL,13,F"Weak sentencing just encourages this
OL,14,Fsort of extremist behaviour."
OL,16,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,17,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,18,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,19,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
